SKELETON MEZZANINE APP FOR HEROKU

Serves static files direct from Heroku - but can't upload media at the moment (working on using S3 now)

Once installed, run locally 'heroku run python manage.py createdb' to create tables and superuser


Thanks to these great blog posts/sites:

